{"title":"应当这样看山（外一首）","authors":["苗得雨"],"dates":[{"year":1985,"month":9,"day":25}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"应当这样看山（外一首）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"苗得雨"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"应当这样看山，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"它生活在阔大空间；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"应这样看山上的树，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"它在阔大的空间中发展。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不要担心耕地有限，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"生活是立体，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不是平面，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"怎不知天上可掉银钱？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"让思想的大门敞向云间！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"写山中大黑石这么多大黑石，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在大山洼里积聚。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不知哪一块能砌坝？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不知哪一块能筑堤？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不知哪一块可垒墙？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不知哪一块当厚基？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"还有，哪些块可供雕刻？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在等候知音者的赏识？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"象估不透那些学龄前儿童，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"谁将作梁，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"谁将作柱，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"谁是将，谁是帅，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"谁作茧，谁抽丝……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他们是待出山的木，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他们是备挑选的材，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他们未来的出息，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"暂时存放在这里。"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}